data.description: NOW AVAILABLE, a 3Bd/2Bth home in Bocage Subdivision! This beautiful abode welcomes you with an easy flow layout, 1,867 HSF, cool tone colors, dual dining spaces adjacent to the kitchen, and statement gas log fireplace. The kitchen offers a deep pantry, granite tile counter tops, matching appliances, and breakfast bar great for entertaining. The primary bedroom suite is complete with a deep closet, dual lavatories, and stall shower with separate whirlpool tub. Special touches illuminate the outdoor spaces with a covered back patio, custom pergola, architectural shingle roof, .27 acres and settled landscaping including a fenced backyard. Merely minutes away from shopping and dining, entertaining is simple in this bocage home. (Last 2 pending contracts feel through at no fault of the seller or reasons toward the home. Home has been fully inspected twice.)
